ed Hitchcock]]\n* [[George Miller (director)|George Miller]]\n* [[Bob Rafelson]]\n* [[Jack Clayton]]\n* [[Alejandro Jodorowsky]]\n* [[Franklin J. Schaffner]]\n* [[Luis Bu\u00f1uel]]\n* [[Costa-Gavras]]\n* [[Bernardo Bertolucci]]\n* [[Bob Fosse]]\n* [[Richard Donner]]\n* [[Elia Kazan]]\n* [[Norman Jewison]]\n* [[Peter Weir]]\n!\n|}\n\n===Musicians===\n{{Div col|colwidth=15em}}\n* [[Lynn Anderson]]\n* [[Paul Anka]]\n* [[Chet Atkins]]\n* [[Joan Baez]]\n* [[Jeff Beck]]\n* [[Tony Bennett]]\n* [[George Benson]]\n* [[Pat Boone]]\n* [[David Bowie]]\n* [[James Brown]]\n* [[Jackson Browne]]\n* [[Jimmy Buffett]]\n* [[Jerry Butler]]\n* [[Glen Campbell]]\n* [[Johnny Cash]]\n* [[Ray Charles]]\n* [[Sonny & Cher]]\n* [[Eric Clapton]]\n* [[Roy Clark]]\n* [[Joe Cocker]]\n* [[David Allan Coe]]\n* [[Leonard Cohen]]\n* [[Rita Coolidge]]\n* [[Alice Cooper]]\n* [[Elvis Costello]]\n* [[Jim Croce]]\n* [[Roger Daltrey]]\n* [[Charlie Daniels]]\n* [[Bobby Darin]]\n* [[Miles Davis]]\n* [[Neil Diamond]]\n* [[John Denver]]\n* [[George Duke]]\n* [[Bob Dylan]]\n* [[Peter Frampton]]\n* [[Bryan Ferry]]\n* [[Roberta Flack]]\n* [[Aretha Franklin]]\n* [[Marvin Gaye]]\n* [[Crystal Gayle]]\n* [[Simon & Garfunkel]]\n* [[Hall & Oates]]\n* [[Merle Haggard]]\n* [[George Harrison]]\n* [[Emmylou Harris]]\n* [[Isaac Hayes]]\n* [[Etta James]]\n* [[Al Jarreau]]\n* [[Waylon Jennings]]\n* [[Janis Joplin]]\n* [[Elton John]]\n* [[George Jones]]\n* [[Quincy Jones]]\n* [[Tom Jones (singer)|Tom Jones]]\n* [[B.B. King]]\n* [[Carole King]]\n* [[Kris Kristofferson]]\n* [[Brenda Lee]]\n* [[Jerry Lee Lewis]]\n* [[John Lennon]]\n* [[Gordon Lightfoot]]\n* [[Meat Loaf]]\n* [[Kenny Loggins]]\n* [[Loretta Lynn]]\n* [[Barry Manilow]]\n* [[Bob Marley]]\n* [[Johnny Mathis]]\n* [[Curtis Mayfield]]\n* [[Don McLean]]\n* [[Roger Miller]]\n* [[Johnny Mitchell]]\n* [[Van Morrison]]\n* [[Anne Murray]]\n* [[Willie Nelson]]\n* [[Olivia Newton-John]]\n* [[Ted Nugent]]\n* [[Roy Orbison]]\n* [[Buck Owens]]\n* [[Iggy Pop]]\n* [[Dolly Parton]]\n* 